{{quote|Here's me being honest with you, Jon Snow, which is more than you've ever done for me. My people have bled enough. We're not here to conquer, we're here to hide behind your Wall, just like you. We need your tunnel. Now, we both know that winter is coming - and if my people aren't south of the Wall when it comes in earnest, we'll all end up worse than dead.|Mance Rayder to [[Jon Snow]]|The Children}}
'''Mance Rayder''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 3|third]], [[Season 4|fourth]] and [[Season 5|fifth]] seasons. He is mentioned in the [[Season 1|first]] and [[Season 2|second]] seasons. He makes his first on-screen appearance in &quot;[[Valar Dohaeris]]&quot; and is played by [[CiarĂĄn Hinds]].&lt;ref&gt;[http://winteriscoming.net/2012/05/ew-scoop-on-s3-the-reeds-are-in-and-so-is-blackfish/ Winter is Coming.net article on season 3 roles]&lt;/ref&gt;&lt;ref&gt;Hibberd, James (August 17, 2012). [http://insidetv.ew.com/2012/08/17/game-of-thrones-mance-rayder/ Game of Thrones' Mance Rayder]. Entertainment Weekly.&lt;/ref&gt; He is the leader of the [[Free Folk]] and a feared opponent of the [[Night's Watch]].

